<Sect1 Id="ReadAMessageTA">
<Title>To Read a Mail Message</Title>
<IndexTerm>
<Primary>reading messages</Primary>
</IndexTerm>
<IndexTerm>
<Primary>messages, reading</Primary>
</IndexTerm>
<ItemizedList Mark="&bull;">
<ListItem Id="HMLR.TSKS.item.31">
<Para>Select the message to be viewed from the Message Header list.
The text of the message appears in the Message View.
</Para>
<Para><Emphasis>Or,</Emphasis>
</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem Id="HMLR.TSKS.item.32">
<Para>Double-click on the message to open it into a separate window.</Para>
<Para>The message remains in the separate window
even when you select another message in your Inbox. The Edit and
Attachments menus become available.
</Para>
</ListItem>
</ItemizedList>
<Procedure>
<Title>See Also</Title>
