<Para>Make sure your mailbox is open on the desktop and its
Message Header list is visible.
</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem Id="HMLR.TSKS.item.199">
<Para>Open two or three frequently used mailboxes on the desktop
making sure you can see the Message Header list.
</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem Id="HMLR.TSKS.item.200">
<Para>Select the message to be copied.
</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem Id="HMLR.TSKS.item.201">
<Para>Drag the message and drop it onto the appropriate mailbox Message Header
List. If you hold down the Control key during the drag and drop, the
message is copied. If you do not hold down Control, the message is
moved.
</Para>
</ListItem>
</OrderedList>
